{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"83fb057b6b","title":"苏联的战略重点在欧洲和中东","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eb17901a01","index":0,"year":1975,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"83fb057b6b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"252cad6c61","type":"title","text":"苏联的战略重点在欧洲和中东","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"47de13946b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：欧洲人来，我都劝他们要注意芬联。现在的世界不太平，不安宁。你们不要怕我们，我们不会侵略到你们欧洲去。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"0298897ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"莱奥·廷德曼斯（以下简称廷）：我正是接受了你们的友好邀请才来访问的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"0ff07fee88","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我希望你们团结起来。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"1c49b4f5c5","type":"paragraph","text":"廷：我们两个人都在致力于实现欧洲团结。我认为我们这一代人的主要任务就是实现欧洲、西欧的统一，实现欧洲一体化。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"aadafe6525","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这个好，我们赞成。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"4b18165337","type":"paragraph","text":"廷：我可以提一个问题吗？主席先生曾两次去过莫斯科，你是什么时候发现不能再和苏联友好下去的？","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"f667b76c01","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：他们驾我们，毁了合同，撤了人员。他们偏祖印度人，反对我们。他们要来，我们就不客气。现在是打舌仗。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"6598b26bd3","type":"paragraph","text":"他们现在还不敢侵略中国。我看他们主要的战略重点在欧洲，中东。我不是叶你们，我是希望你们注意，不然会吃苏联人的亏。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"},{"id":"80560382eb","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东会见比利时首相莱奥·廷德曼斯时谈话的一部分。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b"}],"page":{"id":"f64077a002","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"83fb057b6b","start":545,"end":545}}}},"__N_SSG":true}